National Chairman of Zango Urban Development Association (ZUDA) Alhaji Shehu Aminu Abdullahi has refuted allegations by the Atyap Community Development Association (ACDA) describing Zango Urban as a banditsâ€™ hideout. The chairman, in a statement issued in Kaduna described the allegations as baseless and capable of creating animosity and tension among the people of the Zango area of Southern Kaduna. He challenged the Atyap to name the criminals element in Zango Urban that provide cover for bandits in the area. 